Well, I was talking to John about how excellent my first day in London is going to be.

00:00:37.380 --> 00:00:38.520
I’m doing the traditional side of London

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:41.160
which is going to be the fish and chips, grouse baked potatoes. 

