I’m counting at least 20-25 of them. 

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:56.040
And now you’re going to see his whole library… it is huge! 

00:05:56.040 --> 00:06:00.480
All right, so… yes, it’s a passion. Yeah!  Passion.

