Chef Mark Hix has gifted me two of his lovely cook books. 

00:06:19.840 --> 00:06:24.760
Look at both of them. Both talk about traditional British food, regional British cuisine.

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:29.680
At the same time Chef Mark Hix’s great collection. Well, I am lucky!

